data.description: Cozy, traditional El Monte home.  Same owner for decades. Nice setback. Enormous rear lot. Detached garage could be ADU opportunity (Check with City.)  Original wood floors throughout.  Living room with brick fireplace. Large dining room. Galley style kitchen with lovely eating area. Main bathroom has double sinks, tub, and stall shower. 3rd bedroom has sliders to fabulous, large, covered patio. New roof 2019. Newer water heater and HVAC. Close proximity to 10 and 605 freeways, Houses of Worship, schools, eateries, shopping centers.
